Emmanuel Shinkut Daniel (amụrụ n'ụbọchị iri na asaa nke ọnwa Disemba afọ 1993) bụ onye Naijiria na-eche goolu bọọlụ. Ọ gbara Naijiria na Egwuregwu Afrịka nke afọ 2015  na 2016 Summer Olympics.
Daniel nwetara oku mbụ ya n'akụkụ ndị okenye nke mgbapụta Naịjirịa maka iko mba ụwa nke afọ 2018 megide Zambia n'ọnwa Ọktoba afọ 2016.
Àtụ:Nigeria men's football squad 2016 Summer Olympics
